    "name": "Hemolysis QoI experimental validation requirement",
    "description": "For a Class III VAD device at MRL 5, absolute hemolysis index predictions must be verified against physical bench-test measurements using a standardised haemolysis protocol (ASTM F1841 or equivalent). The required verification method is experimental-validation; computational surrogates alone do not satisfy this requirement.",
