    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-lead-assessor",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 credibility factors. While achieved levels fall below required levels for the majority of factors, the team accepted the package on the basis that the high-fidelity numerical simulation provides results that are functionally equivalent to experimental validation for the hemolysis QoI. The simulation reproduces bench-test boundary conditions with less than 3% deviation in bulk flow metrics and Monte Carlo uncertainty bounds remain well within the clinical threshold. The team noted that the Requirement specifying experimental-validation as the required verification method is satisfied in substance, if not in strict method, by the companion simulation. No formal method substitution was documented.",
